enhanced_by.reason: The relaxed method relies on the state set by addTags to define allowed tags.
The relaxed method relies on the state set by addAttributes to define allowed attributes for tags.
The relaxed method relies on the state set by addProtocols to define allowed protocols for attributes.
Both relaxed and isSafeTag methods deal with tag safety and can be used to assert the safety of tags after calling relaxed.
Both relaxed and isSafeAttribute methods deal with attribute safety and can be used to assert the safety of attributes after calling relaxed.
Both relaxed and getEnforcedAttributes methods deal with attribute enforcement and can be used to assert enforced attributes after calling relaxed.
